00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:22.920 line:80%
FUNERAL CORTEGE OF HE JINGYUAN
LOYAL AND UPRIGHT GENERAL OF DAYIN

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.720 line:80%
MEMORIAL OFFERING

00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:27.560 line:80%
SPIRIT TABLET OF HE JINGYUAN
GOVERNOR OF JIZHOU

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:36.880 line:80%
-General He, may you rest in peace.
-General He, may you rest in peace.

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:44.080 line:80%
General He, may your spirit rest in peace.

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:03.000 line:80%
General He…

00:01:05.160 --> 00:01:06.360 line:80%
rest in peace.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:19.480 line:20%
WEI QILIN, CRIMINAL OF DAYIN

00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:23.520 line:80%
Wei Qilin!

00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:25.960 line:80%
You treacherous traitor!

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:30.240 line:20%
He tried to run. Served him right
when he went over the cliff

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:31.160 line:20%
with his whole family!

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:32.680 line:20%
He deserved it!

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:34.640 line:80%
And now, even General He
has died on the battlefield,

00:01:34.720 --> 00:01:36.520 line:80%
-all because of that traitor!
-Beat him!

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.920 line:80%
-Beat that traitor!
-Beat him!

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:42.520 line:80%
Burn him! Send him below to beg
the two generals' forgiveness.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:48.840 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:54.040 line:80%
You are the woman general

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:56.600 line:80%
who killed Prince Changxin, are you not?

00:01:57.480 --> 00:01:58.440 line:80%
-Yes.
-That is her.

00:01:58.520 --> 00:02:00.520 line:80%
-Yes, Mrs. Fan.
-It's her.

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:03.520 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, why did you stop us?

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:04.640 line:80%
We are burning that traitor!

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:08.120 line:80%
He is not a traitor.

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:09.200 line:80%
Mrs. Fan,

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.920 line:80%
we respect you.

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:14.520 line:80%
A woman who faced death
and slew Prince Changxin.

00:02:14.600 --> 00:02:16.080 line:80%
But why would you defend Wei Qilin,

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:17.320 line:80%
that traitor?

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:18.960 line:80%
-I'm--
-Why?

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:20.080 line:80%
Why are you speaking for him?

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.880 line:80%
He is not. He is not a traitor.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:25.480 line:80%
Today is the memorial
for Old General Xie and General He.

00:02:25.560 --> 00:02:26.400 line:80%
What you are doing now

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:29.240 line:80%
is turning against the entire Jizhou
and Yanzhou army!

00:02:29.320 --> 00:02:30.920 line:80%
Forgive me, Generals.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:33.360 line:80%
-But that is not the truth.
-Enough of your nonsense!

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:35.600 line:80%
That is enough!

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:41.520 line:80%
-Marquis.
-Marquis.

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:52.880 line:80%
Let's go.

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:04.040 line:80%
I haven't paid my respects
to the late General Xie.

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:06.400 line:80%
I truly came to honor him.

00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:08.560 line:80%
If you defend that traitor,

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:10.680 line:80%
then you have no right
to bow before General Xie!

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:13.040 line:80%
The Xie army will never allow it!

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:14.360 line:80%
-That is right!
-Never!

00:03:14.440 --> 00:03:16.040 line:80%
-Get out!
-Get out!

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:16.960 line:80%
Form ranks!

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:41.960 line:80%
Marquis, what are you…

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:46.360 line:80%
-Marquis, she just--
-Xie army! Yanzhou army! Hear my command!

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:50.160 line:80%
Kneel.

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:05.000 line:80%
Generals,

00:04:06.760 --> 00:04:07.600 line:80%
may you rest in peace.

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:52.280 line:20%
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>ZHU YU</i>
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:58.080 line:80%
JIZHOU YAMEN

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:12.920 line:80%
Changyu.

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.600 line:80%
Are you feeling better?

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.320 line:80%
Commoner Fan Changyu

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:33.160 line:80%
greets the Marquis.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:38.040 line:80%
What did you

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:40.520 line:80%
just call me?

00:06:42.520 --> 00:06:43.720 line:80%
Marquis.

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:46.600 line:80%
After all this time,

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:48.560 line:80%
that is what you settled on?

00:06:53.880 --> 00:06:55.480 line:80%
One word, Marquis…

00:06:57.920 --> 00:06:59.800 line:80%
and suddenly we are strangers.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.560 line:80%
If the Marquis finds it too distant,

00:07:03.400 --> 00:07:04.880 line:80%
then since we share the same teacher,

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.520 line:80%
you may call me Junior.

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:16.880 line:80%
Marquis, this is a private residence
and my own chamber.

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:18.600 line:80%
Please keep your distance.

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:22.760 line:80%
I think I know

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.600 line:80%
what troubles you.

00:07:26.520 --> 00:07:27.680 line:80%
But you should also know

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:30.840 line:80%
there is nothing in this world
that could make us strangers.

00:07:32.040 --> 00:07:33.320 line:80%
And what if the matter

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:35.480 line:80%
were serious enough

00:07:36.320 --> 00:07:38.240 line:80%
to cost you your command
of the Yanzhou army?

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:49.240 line:80%
Whether I am fit to command an army

00:07:49.760 --> 00:07:51.120 line:80%
depends solely on my own ability.

00:07:51.200 --> 00:07:53.960 line:80%
It has nothing to do
with anyone or anything.

00:07:54.680 --> 00:07:55.640 line:80%
Including you.

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.120 line:80%
So in your view,

00:07:59.080 --> 00:08:00.360 line:80%
everything in this world

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:04.160 line:80%
is like matters of the army…

00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:09.080 line:80%
and in the end,
you alone decide everything.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:27.160 line:80%
It is late.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.320 line:80%
I still need to tend to my wounds.

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:31.240 line:80%
Marquis, please leave.

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:02.400 line:80%
JINGHE GATE

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.640 line:80%
Chancellor Wei.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:05.520 line:80%
Chancellor Wei.

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:09.160 line:80%
Grand Tutor.

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:11.480 line:80%
Would you look at that.

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:12.960 line:80%
I must be getting old.

00:09:13.040 --> 00:09:14.560 line:80%
My student has a mind of his own now.

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:16.240 line:80%
I can hardly keep him in line.

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:21.720 line:80%
This matter concerns
the military command of Jizhou.

00:09:21.800 --> 00:09:24.720 line:80%
We weighed it purely on merit in battle.
There was no personal agenda.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:28.480 line:80%
I hope you will not
take offense, Chancellor Wei.

00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:32.680 line:80%
If you truly feel your years
catching up with you,

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:35.480 line:80%
perhaps you should follow Grand Tutor Tao

00:09:35.560 --> 00:09:36.880 line:80%
and bow out while you're ahead.

00:09:37.840 --> 00:09:39.880 line:80%
To this day, the court, the officials,

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:40.840 line:80%
even His Majesty,

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:43.480 line:80%
remember him with nothing but praise.

00:09:43.560 --> 00:09:46.560 line:80%
Far better than clinging
to office well past 70,

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:48.280 line:80%
throwing around seniority

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:50.440 line:80%
while unable to keep things in line.

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:57.000 line:80%
Arrogant, is he?

00:09:57.920 --> 00:09:59.880 line:80%
We lost General He
in the Battle of Lucheng.

00:10:00.680 --> 00:10:02.680 line:80%
In his last words, he strongly recommended

00:10:02.760 --> 00:10:04.680 line:80%
Li Huai'an as the military administrator.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:08.640 line:80%
Now that the military command
of Jizhou has slipped from his grasp,

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:11.560 line:80%
Wei Yan's arrogance
may not last much longer.

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:15.720 line:80%
As long as Marquis Wu'an continues
to station his army in Lucheng,

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:20.440 line:80%
control of the troops
will not pass into other hands.

00:10:20.520 --> 00:10:21.560 line:80%
And that

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:24.760 line:80%
is precisely
where Wei Yan's confidence lies.

00:10:24.840 --> 00:10:28.560 line:20%
HALL OF LETTERS

00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:40.520 line:80%
<i>Mother,</i>

00:10:40.600 --> 00:10:44.720 line:80%
<i>I'll never play the traitor game</i>
<i>with them again.</i>

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:48.440 line:80%
They are only children.

00:10:49.160 --> 00:10:50.160 line:80%
What do they know?

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:53.520 line:80%
In this world, how many people

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:55.800 line:80%
can truly tell loyalty from treachery,

00:10:56.440 --> 00:10:57.400 line:80%
or right from wrong?

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.120 line:80%
Dinner is ready.

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:12.280 line:80%
All right. Let's go eat.

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:31.560 line:80%
<i>Father. Mother.</i>

00:11:32.520 --> 00:11:34.600 line:80%
<i>What is all this really about?</i>

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:40.080 line:80%
Come in.

00:11:41.520 --> 00:11:42.480 line:80%
-Fan!
-Changyu!

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:43.520 line:80%
Changyu!

00:11:44.400 --> 00:11:45.240 line:80%
Changyu!

00:11:46.880 --> 00:11:49.840 line:80%
-What is all this?
-It has been days now.

00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:51.880 line:80%
-General Fan looks well enough to drink.
-Exactly.

00:11:51.960 --> 00:11:53.800 line:80%
We have been waiting all this time.

00:11:53.880 --> 00:11:56.680 line:80%
We have been eager to come
celebrate with you. Have we not?

00:11:56.760 --> 00:11:58.360 line:80%
General Fan?

00:11:58.440 --> 00:11:59.760 line:80%
You flatter me too much.

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:01.880 line:80%
In our eyes, you are a true general.

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:03.800 line:80%
Killing Prince Changxin was no small feat.

00:12:03.880 --> 00:12:05.320 line:80%
Chongzhou will soon be ours.

00:12:05.400 --> 00:12:07.400 line:80%
After that, there'll be
no battles left to fight.

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:08.400 line:80%
-That is right.
-Exactly.

00:12:08.480 --> 00:12:09.800 line:80%
-Come on. Drink up.
-Come. Changyu.

00:12:09.880 --> 00:12:11.080 line:80%
-Let me fill your cup.
-Fill it up.

00:12:12.880 --> 00:12:13.720 line:80%
Here you go.

00:12:15.040 --> 00:12:16.440 line:80%
Then I thank you all.

00:12:16.520 --> 00:12:17.560 line:80%
Cheers.

00:12:17.640 --> 00:12:18.560 line:80%
-Cheers!
-Drink!

00:12:19.600 --> 00:12:20.440 line:80%
Changyu!

00:12:24.440 --> 00:12:25.520 line:80%
-Drink…
-Changyu.

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.040 line:80%
Lord Li is here asking to see you.

00:12:28.520 --> 00:12:29.360 line:80%
Let him in.

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:32.160 line:80%
That may not be appropriate.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:34.200 line:80%
Changyu, you should go out and see him.

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:37.960 line:80%
HALL OF LETTERS

00:12:42.320 --> 00:12:44.600 line:80%
Lord Li, what are you doing?

00:12:45.480 --> 00:12:46.560 line:80%
I am ashamed.

00:12:47.240 --> 00:12:49.920 line:80%
I have come today to beg your forgiveness.

00:12:50.520 --> 00:12:51.640 line:80%
My first offense.

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:54.560 line:80%
When the rebels attacked the city,

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:57.680 line:80%
you knocked me unconscious
because you feared I might act rashly.

00:12:58.440 --> 00:12:59.600 line:80%
Yet I didn't understand.

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:03.040 line:80%
Instead, when you were gravely ill,
I spoke harshly to you.

00:13:04.360 --> 00:13:05.400 line:80%
That was unjust.

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:07.720 line:80%
My second offense.

00:13:08.400 --> 00:13:10.800 line:80%
Our dispute led others
to misunderstand you,

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:13.040 line:80%
damaging your reputation.

00:13:13.640 --> 00:13:14.840 line:80%
That was discourteous.

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:17.360 line:80%
So I beg you

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:20.240 line:80%
to strike me with these brambles.

00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:23.480 line:80%
Otherwise, I won't be able to face you

00:13:24.520 --> 00:13:26.520 line:80%
or General He again.

00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:44.080 line:80%
Please do not dwell on it.

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:45.560 line:80%
General He treated me well.

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:47.600 line:80%
I understand the position you were in.

00:13:48.520 --> 00:13:49.800 line:80%
-Please get up.
-I am ashamed.

00:13:50.920 --> 00:13:52.960 line:80%
I thought the northwest had made me wiser.

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:55.920 line:80%
Yet I'm not as clear-headed as you.

00:13:56.640 --> 00:13:58.280 line:80%
You care too much to think straight.

00:13:59.560 --> 00:14:00.840 line:80%
You're too hard on yourself.

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:05.800 line:80%
Besides, I was wrong to knock you out.

00:14:06.400 --> 00:14:08.000 line:80%
One fault cancels the other.

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:09.080 line:80%
We are even now.

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:11.280 line:80%
Get up.

00:14:18.160 --> 00:14:21.200 line:80%
Counting soldiers, choosing generals,
riding horses, going to war.

00:14:21.280 --> 00:14:22.680 line:80%
I will draw this one.

00:14:22.760 --> 00:14:23.720 line:80%
No peeking.

00:14:23.800 --> 00:14:24.640 line:80%
EASTERN OUTSKIRTS OF QINGPING COUNTY

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:26.160 line:80%
I am drawing the highest card.

00:14:26.680 --> 00:14:28.160 line:80%
Look. Twin Heavens!

00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:29.880 line:80%
I got four pairs of candied hawthorns!

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:33.360 line:80%
-Look at this. Did I win?
-I won!

00:14:33.440 --> 00:14:35.920 line:80%
-I won!
-It is me. I won!

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:37.720 line:80%
-Who won this round?
-Mr. Zhao, look.

00:14:37.800 --> 00:14:39.000 line:80%
Tell us who won.

00:14:39.080 --> 00:14:41.400 line:80%
Twin Heavens outrank the great houses.

00:14:41.480 --> 00:14:42.720 line:80%
Bao'er wins this round.

00:14:44.440 --> 00:14:45.280 line:80%
Come on.

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:47.760 line:80%
-Again.
-Let's play another round.

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:50.120 line:80%
-All right. That is enough.
-Thunder God! Boom, you're done!

00:14:50.200 --> 00:14:51.920 line:80%
I want the Empress card.

00:15:06.600 --> 00:15:07.440 line:80%
Come here.

00:15:08.320 --> 00:15:09.240 line:80%
Do not run.

00:15:10.520 --> 00:15:11.720 line:80%
It is one of ours.

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:25.920 line:20%
THATCHED COTTAGE

00:15:33.680 --> 00:15:34.560 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:36.840 line:80%
Ning!

00:15:41.120 --> 00:15:42.720 line:80%
Pretty Lady!

00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:51.000 line:80%
Mother, you are finally back!

00:15:51.680 --> 00:15:52.920 line:80%
I missed you so much!

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:56.520 line:80%
I missed you too.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:16:00.000 line:80%
Ms. Yu.

00:16:00.560 --> 00:16:02.080 line:80%
You are back.

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:14.120 line:80%
Changyu asked General Xie Qi
to escort me home.

00:16:14.720 --> 00:16:16.680 line:80%
She said no one in Lin'an
is to be left behind.

00:16:17.880 --> 00:16:18.760 line:80%
And I am

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:21.200 line:80%
one of you.

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:23.680 line:80%
Changyu really is something.

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:27.040 line:80%
First she sent me,
Changning, and Bao'er home.

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:30.880 line:80%
-Now she has brought back another.
-It is good you are back.

00:16:30.960 --> 00:16:34.120 line:80%
-That's one missing piece home.
-Yes, indeed.

00:16:39.360 --> 00:16:40.800 line:20%
TEN DAYS LATER

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:42.000 line:20%
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

00:17:14.360 --> 00:17:15.520 line:80%
Why are you still here?

00:17:16.040 --> 00:17:18.360 line:80%
-What?
-Come on.

00:17:35.480 --> 00:17:36.320 line:80%
Speak.

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:38.960 line:80%
Marquis Wu'an sent word
that military matters are pressing.

00:17:39.040 --> 00:17:40.720 line:80%
He cannot attend.
He said not to wait for him.

00:17:44.240 --> 00:17:46.560 line:80%
Eunuch, if the decree
is not announced soon,

00:17:46.640 --> 00:17:48.320 line:80%
we will miss the auspicious hour.

00:17:53.960 --> 00:17:56.000 line:80%
Very well. We will wait no longer.

00:17:57.040 --> 00:17:58.240 line:80%
Then,

00:18:00.120 --> 00:18:01.960 line:80%
we will announce the first two decrees.

00:18:02.040 --> 00:18:04.800 line:80%
HALL OF LETTERS

00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:06.680 line:80%
Where are we going? I have meat stewing.

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:07.640 line:80%
Come on.

00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:19.920 line:80%
-Where were you?
-Everyone is here.

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:20.880 line:80%
Finally.

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:32.760 line:80%
-How long does it take to read the decree?
-Shh!

00:18:33.280 --> 00:18:34.800 line:80%
In those puppet plays,

00:18:34.880 --> 00:18:36.120 line:80%
it only takes a moment.

00:18:36.200 --> 00:18:38.400 line:80%
Why is it taking so long now?

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:40.240 line:80%
I didn't even kneel this long
for my grandpa.

00:18:40.320 --> 00:18:41.720 line:80%
My legs are completely numb.

00:18:41.800 --> 00:18:42.960 line:80%
Get lost.

00:18:45.480 --> 00:18:46.560 line:80%
My stew…

00:18:47.080 --> 00:18:48.680 line:80%
HALL OF ARMS

00:18:57.080 --> 00:19:00.960 line:80%
Imperial decree!

00:19:02.960 --> 00:19:06.000 line:80%
All soldiers, receive the decree.

00:19:07.440 --> 00:19:10.400 line:80%
"By command of His Majesty.

00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:11.640 line:80%
The rebels of Chongzhou

00:19:11.720 --> 00:19:14.000 line:80%
have thrown the realm into chaos

00:19:14.080 --> 00:19:15.120 line:80%
and oppressed the people.

00:19:15.840 --> 00:19:19.480 line:80%
Governor He Jingyuan of Jizhou
upheld the realm,

00:19:19.560 --> 00:19:21.200 line:80%
slew the rebels,

00:19:21.280 --> 00:19:24.760 line:80%
and fell heroically in battle.

00:19:24.840 --> 00:19:26.880 line:80%
Moved by his loyalty,

00:19:26.960 --> 00:19:28.760 line:80%
His Majesty now posthumously grants him

00:19:28.840 --> 00:19:32.640 line:80%
the title Grand General Kuangzheng.

00:19:32.720 --> 00:19:36.120 line:80%
A state funeral shall be held

00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:39.800 line:80%
to honor his loyalty
and console his spirit.

00:19:39.880 --> 00:19:43.240 line:80%
Let this be proclaimed
throughout the realm so that all may know.

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:47.920 line:80%
Zhenwei Commandant of Jizhou, Li Huai'an,

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:50.040 line:80%
rendered great service

00:19:50.120 --> 00:19:51.480 line:80%
in defending the city.

00:19:51.560 --> 00:19:54.040 line:80%
He is hereby appointed
Military Administrator of Jizhou.

00:19:54.120 --> 00:19:57.360 line:20%
Two hundred taels of gold
and 800 taels of silver

00:19:57.440 --> 00:20:00.760 line:20%
are awarded to Li Huai'an and his troops."

00:20:00.840 --> 00:20:01.920 line:20%
We thank His Majesty.

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:14.800 line:80%
"Jizhou soldier Fan Changyu."

00:20:18.600 --> 00:20:19.680 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:22.240 line:80%
Where did Changyu go?

00:20:22.320 --> 00:20:23.480 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:20:24.080 --> 00:20:25.960 line:80%
-I do not know.
-"Fan Changyu.

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:33.120 line:80%
Jizhou soldier

00:20:34.200 --> 00:20:35.360 line:80%
Fan Changyu,

00:20:36.160 --> 00:20:38.440 line:80%
for slaying Prince Changxin
on the battlefield

00:20:38.520 --> 00:20:40.120 line:80%
and rendering great merit,

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:42.600 line:80%
is hereby appointed Cavalry Captain,

00:20:42.680 --> 00:20:45.040 line:80%
rank fifth class.

00:20:45.120 --> 00:20:47.800 line:80%
One hundred taels of gold
and 500 taels of silver

00:20:47.880 --> 00:20:52.120 line:80%
-are awarded to Fan Changyu and her men.
-Fifth rank!

00:20:52.200 --> 00:20:56.160 line:80%
As the Jizhou army
cannot remain without leadership,

00:20:56.240 --> 00:21:00.400 line:80%
Military Administrator Li Huai'an
shall take command,

00:21:00.480 --> 00:21:04.000 line:80%
with Cavalry Captain Fan Changyu
serving as his deputy.

00:21:04.080 --> 00:21:07.120 line:80%
Together they shall oversee
the military authority of Jizhou

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:09.280 line:80%
to steady the army's morale.

00:21:09.800 --> 00:21:11.880 line:80%
Let this decree be proclaimed.

00:21:11.960 --> 00:21:14.080 line:80%
All shall take heed."

00:21:21.320 --> 00:21:23.200 line:80%
Li Huai'an, receive the decree
on her behalf.

00:21:25.440 --> 00:21:26.640 line:80%
We thank His Majesty.

00:21:29.760 --> 00:21:31.840 line:80%
Congratulations,
Military Administrator Li.

00:21:32.360 --> 00:21:34.920 line:80%
Eunuch, you must be tired
from the journey.

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:37.400 line:80%
If you do not mind,
please stay and rest for a while.

00:21:37.480 --> 00:21:39.200 line:80%
-This way, please.
-Very well.

00:21:44.920 --> 00:21:46.080 line:80%
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

00:21:46.160 --> 00:21:47.040 line:80%
Changyu is an official!

00:21:47.120 --> 00:21:48.400 line:80%
-This is fantastic!
-She made it!

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:49.760 line:80%
Changyu is an official!

00:21:50.280 --> 00:21:51.600 line:80%
-Cavalry Captain!
-Five hundred taels!

00:21:51.680 --> 00:21:53.760 line:80%
I have served in the palace
for so many years,

00:21:53.840 --> 00:21:57.240 line:80%
yet I have never seen
such unruly soldiers.

00:21:57.320 --> 00:21:58.360 line:80%
Those rabble?

00:21:58.440 --> 00:22:01.080 line:80%
How on earth did they manage
to defeat Prince Changxin?

00:22:04.480 --> 00:22:05.920 line:80%
-Captain Fan is over there.
-Come on.

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:06.920 line:80%
Let's go.

00:22:07.880 --> 00:22:08.920 line:80%
Captain Fan.

00:22:09.760 --> 00:22:10.680 line:80%
Captain Fan.

00:22:15.880 --> 00:22:16.720 line:80%
Captain Fan.

00:22:16.800 --> 00:22:19.720 line:80%
Before, we failed to recognize
your greatness. Forgive our offense.

00:22:19.800 --> 00:22:20.640 line:80%
-Forgive us.
-Forgive us.

00:22:20.720 --> 00:22:21.960 line:80%
What did you just call me?

00:22:22.040 --> 00:22:23.520 line:80%
-Captain Fan.
-Changyu!

00:22:24.040 --> 00:22:24.880 line:80%
Where is she?

00:22:26.800 --> 00:22:27.640 line:80%
Congratulations!

00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:28.600 line:80%
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:31.360 line:80%
-You are an official now!
-Official? What kind of official?

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:33.680 line:80%
Cavalry Captain. An imperial appointment.

00:22:34.200 --> 00:22:35.560 line:80%
-Fifth rank.
-Fifth rank.

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:38.560 line:80%
Since the dynasty's founding,
no woman has held such rank.

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:39.520 line:80%
And that's not all.

00:22:39.600 --> 00:22:40.920 line:80%
Even the county magistrate

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:43.520 line:80%
will have to bow three times
before speaking to you.

00:22:43.600 --> 00:22:45.120 line:80%
Just imagine the prestige.

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:46.040 line:80%
Really?

00:22:46.120 --> 00:22:48.920 line:80%
-You are truly a woman general now.
-As long as we follow Changyu,

00:22:49.000 --> 00:22:51.160 line:80%
-we will be feasting every day.
-Exactly.

00:22:51.240 --> 00:22:52.560 line:80%
We will want for nothing!

00:22:52.640 --> 00:22:54.960 line:80%
But remember, all of this
is thanks to Changyu.

00:22:55.040 --> 00:22:56.840 line:80%
From today on, I'm no longer Jin Yuanbao.

00:22:56.920 --> 00:22:58.520 line:80%
My new name is Jin Triumph.

00:22:58.600 --> 00:23:00.400 line:80%
The three of them are changing theirs too.

00:23:00.480 --> 00:23:01.520 line:80%
-Man Legion.
-Right.

00:23:01.600 --> 00:23:02.800 line:80%
Man Banner and Man Valor.

00:23:03.400 --> 00:23:06.200 line:80%
That sounds great.
I am treating everyone to stewed meat!

00:23:09.040 --> 00:23:11.400 line:80%
-Come on. Give her a hand.
-Come on.

00:23:11.480 --> 00:23:13.240 line:80%
Sit down. Go sit over there.

00:23:13.320 --> 00:23:15.040 line:80%
All right.

00:23:15.120 --> 00:23:16.640 line:80%
Changyu, let me get you a bowl.

00:23:16.720 --> 00:23:18.960 line:80%
-Triumph, sit here.
-I will pour the wine.

00:23:19.720 --> 00:23:20.560 line:80%
Here.

00:23:22.560 --> 00:23:23.920 line:80%
-Pass it over.
-All right.

00:23:25.120 --> 00:23:27.640 line:80%
-Here.
-Thank you.

00:23:28.560 --> 00:23:29.880 line:80%
-Come on.
-All right.

00:23:29.960 --> 00:23:31.280 line:80%
Not too much. Two big bowls will do.

00:23:31.360 --> 00:23:32.200 line:80%
Take it over.

00:23:32.280 --> 00:23:33.240 line:80%
Here.

00:23:33.840 --> 00:23:35.000 line:80%
Everyone,

00:23:35.560 --> 00:23:38.120 line:80%
-enjoy yourselves.
-That is a generous portion.

00:23:38.200 --> 00:23:40.200 line:80%
-Please enjoy yourselves.
-Bottoms up.

00:23:40.280 --> 00:23:41.280 line:80%
Let me fill your cup.

00:23:54.760 --> 00:23:56.800 line:80%
Administrator Li,
you must be rather disappointed.

00:23:58.080 --> 00:23:59.760 line:80%
You thought that once General He passed,

00:24:00.360 --> 00:24:02.040 line:80%
the military command

00:24:02.120 --> 00:24:04.280 line:80%
would naturally fall
into the Li clan's hands.

00:24:04.360 --> 00:24:06.760 line:80%
Yet in the end, half of it slipped away.

00:24:09.240 --> 00:24:10.920 line:80%
Such a trivial matter
would never disappoint me.

00:24:12.320 --> 00:24:13.320 line:80%
What puzzles me is you.

00:24:13.400 --> 00:24:15.720 line:80%
The military command of Jizhou
is never small.

00:24:15.800 --> 00:24:17.960 line:80%
Why would you entrust it to a young woman

00:24:18.040 --> 00:24:19.960 line:80%
with neither experience nor backing?

00:24:27.720 --> 00:24:30.120 line:80%
Was it not you who filed
for her achievements to the court?

00:24:31.520 --> 00:24:32.880 line:80%
This is simply the outcome.

00:24:35.560 --> 00:24:38.280 line:80%
I credited her merits to protect her.

00:24:39.160 --> 00:24:40.600 line:80%
And I will continue to protect her.

00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:48.080 line:80%
My wife has no need
for protection from an outsider.

00:24:48.160 --> 00:24:49.120 line:80%
Your wife?

00:24:50.600 --> 00:24:53.360 line:80%
If I remember correctly,
Fan Changyu married Yan Zheng,

00:24:53.440 --> 00:24:54.360 line:80%
not you, Xie Zheng.

00:24:54.880 --> 00:24:57.520 line:80%
And even as Yan Zheng,
you two signed a divorce letter.

00:24:57.600 --> 00:25:00.120 line:80%
As things stand,
she has no marriage bond with you at all.

00:25:00.200 --> 00:25:02.800 line:80%
Marquis, why deceive yourself?

00:25:08.120 --> 00:25:09.480 line:80%
Administrator Li, do not forget

00:25:10.560 --> 00:25:12.560 line:80%
your betrothal to the Grand Princess.

00:25:13.560 --> 00:25:15.160 line:80%
A gentleman

00:25:15.240 --> 00:25:16.480 line:80%
doesn't play both sides.

00:25:35.320 --> 00:25:37.320 line:80%
Xie Qi has safely escorted
Yu Qianqian back.

00:25:37.400 --> 00:25:39.680 line:80%
As for Grand Tutor Tao,
he insists on staying.

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:42.720 line:80%
No matter what we say,
he refuses to return to office.

00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:44.520 line:80%
If he does not go back,

00:25:45.040 --> 00:25:47.000 line:80%
His Majesty may not take kindly to it.

00:25:47.080 --> 00:25:47.920 line:80%
That's no matter.

00:25:49.640 --> 00:25:52.440 line:80%
His Majesty has always been one
to sway with the wind,

00:25:52.520 --> 00:25:53.880 line:80%
clinging to whoever holds power.

00:25:56.840 --> 00:25:57.760 line:80%
There's something else.

00:25:58.560 --> 00:26:01.080 line:80%
The court giving Mrs. Fan
half the military command

00:26:02.200 --> 00:26:05.240 line:80%
is likely the result of the conflict
between Wei Yan and Li Xing.

00:26:06.200 --> 00:26:07.280 line:80%
For years, they've kept

00:26:08.200 --> 00:26:09.320 line:80%
each other in check.

00:26:10.480 --> 00:26:11.840 line:80%
In the end, they simply let go.

00:26:11.920 --> 00:26:14.600 line:80%
To them, Fan Changyu poses no threat.

00:26:15.280 --> 00:26:16.840 line:80%
Better she holds command than I do.

00:26:19.000 --> 00:26:21.200 line:80%
Li Huai'an thought he was being clever,

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:23.680 line:80%
yet ended up a pawn for both sides.

00:26:24.640 --> 00:26:26.160 line:80%
Those two old foxes.

00:26:27.120 --> 00:26:28.680 line:80%
They are scheming so loudly,

00:26:29.400 --> 00:26:31.520 line:80%
we can hear it all the way in Jizhou.

00:26:33.360 --> 00:26:34.400 line:80%
At this rate,

00:26:35.080 --> 00:26:36.960 line:80%
Fan Changyu is like a child carrying gold

00:26:37.040 --> 00:26:38.520 line:80%
through a bustling market.

00:26:41.000 --> 00:26:42.040 line:80%
Trouble will find her soon.

00:26:43.440 --> 00:26:44.640 line:80%
As long as I am here,

00:26:45.800 --> 00:26:47.400 line:80%
no one will trouble her.

00:26:49.040 --> 00:26:49.880 line:80%
What should we do now?

00:26:50.560 --> 00:26:52.800 line:80%
Split the command in two,
and Mrs. Fan gains nothing.

00:26:52.880 --> 00:26:54.400 line:80%
She'll end up taking the fall.

00:26:55.040 --> 00:26:56.840 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li will surely be displeased.

00:26:56.920 --> 00:26:58.440 line:80%
Grandfather intends to use her

00:26:58.520 --> 00:26:59.800 line:80%
to disrupt Wei Yan's plans.

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:01.720 line:80%
But it doesn't matter.
We can simply play along.

00:27:03.480 --> 00:27:04.480 line:80%
I can be the one

00:27:05.040 --> 00:27:07.040 line:80%
supporting Fan Changyu too.

00:27:14.360 --> 00:27:15.360 line:80%
Good heavens!

00:27:16.640 --> 00:27:18.320 line:80%
Cavalry Captain.

00:27:19.080 --> 00:27:21.600 line:80%
One hundred taels of gold
and 500 taels of silver!

00:27:21.680 --> 00:27:22.960 line:80%
Ancestors above!

00:27:23.040 --> 00:27:25.840 line:80%
That'll last Fan Changyu
and Fan Changning a lifetime.

00:27:26.560 --> 00:27:27.680 line:80%
That is nothing.

00:27:27.760 --> 00:27:30.840 line:80%
Captain Fan now commands
half the forces of Jizhou.

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:32.760 line:80%
Xie Qi,

00:27:32.840 --> 00:27:34.080 line:80%
when you return,

00:27:34.160 --> 00:27:36.080 line:80%
please pass a message to Changyu.

00:27:36.160 --> 00:27:37.680 line:80%
Even if she has become a captain,

00:27:37.760 --> 00:27:40.440 line:80%
there's still a saying,
"Don't bite the husband that fed you."

00:27:41.240 --> 00:27:43.680 line:80%
Husband? It's
"Don't bite the hand that fed you."

00:27:44.320 --> 00:27:45.200 line:80%
Stop interrupting.

00:27:45.880 --> 00:27:47.960 line:80%
When Changyu was at her lowest,

00:27:48.040 --> 00:27:51.200 line:80%
it was Yan Zheng who stood by her side.

00:27:51.280 --> 00:27:53.320 line:80%
He was even taken away
by the draft for her sake.

00:27:53.400 --> 00:27:55.720 line:80%
That kind of bond is not ordinary.

00:27:55.800 --> 00:27:57.280 line:80%
Don't let her turn into one

00:27:57.360 --> 00:28:00.240 line:80%
of those women who climb the ladder
and pull it up behind them.

00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:01.320 line:80%
Women? It's normally men who did that.

00:28:01.400 --> 00:28:03.240 line:80%
Why do you keep butting in,

00:28:03.320 --> 00:28:05.560 line:80%
like a water ladle
scooping again and again?

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:08.840 line:80%
If you say something wrong,
should people not correct you?

00:28:09.960 --> 00:28:10.920 line:80%
Mr. and Mrs. Zhao,

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:12.560 line:80%
do not worry.

00:28:12.640 --> 00:28:14.720 line:80%
Changyu is not that kind of person.

00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:19.120 line:80%
I will pass your message to Captain Fan

00:28:19.200 --> 00:28:20.720 line:80%
and to our Mar…

00:28:22.760 --> 00:28:23.640 line:80%
our best comrade.

00:28:25.160 --> 00:28:27.400 line:80%
Tell Yan Zheng to stay safe
and come home soon.

00:28:27.480 --> 00:28:29.200 line:80%
A family should all be under one roof.

00:28:29.280 --> 00:28:32.040 line:80%
That is right. All the people of Lin'an
are waiting for him.

00:28:33.640 --> 00:28:35.840 line:80%
Your words will be delivered.

00:28:37.280 --> 00:28:39.960 line:80%
THE SEA OF LEARNING HAS NO END

00:28:40.560 --> 00:28:43.080 line:80%
I never thought Your Highness
would go so far

00:28:43.160 --> 00:28:44.800 line:80%
for Luyuan Academy's headmaster.

00:28:48.480 --> 00:28:50.480 line:80%
It seems our agreement
was also for his sake.

00:28:52.840 --> 00:28:54.960 line:80%
Lingering in Jizhou
instead of returning to the capital…

00:28:55.480 --> 00:28:57.280 line:80%
Got your eye on another man's wife?

00:28:59.480 --> 00:29:01.720 line:80%
Captain Fan's marriage
to Marquis Wu'an was a sham.

00:29:01.800 --> 00:29:03.640 line:80%
She and I are comrades-in-arms.

00:29:03.720 --> 00:29:04.880 line:80%
Nothing improper between us.

00:29:06.760 --> 00:29:08.920 line:80%
Headmaster and I once fought side by side.

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:11.120 line:80%
Our bond is simply
that of upright comrades.

00:29:14.520 --> 00:29:15.560 line:80%
Captain Fan.

00:29:18.920 --> 00:29:21.840 line:80%
If your intentions are so proper,
why did you panic like that?

00:29:22.440 --> 00:29:23.520 line:80%
You care a lot for a comrade.

00:29:23.600 --> 00:29:25.400 line:80%
Your Highness jests at my expense.

00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:32.360 line:80%
-Mr. Gongsun.
-A joke told twice loses its charm.

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:37.000 line:80%
I didn't expect Your Highness
and Administrator Li here.

00:29:38.600 --> 00:29:40.200 line:80%
It seems I have intruded.

00:29:46.600 --> 00:29:47.440 line:80%
Wenkan.

00:29:49.720 --> 00:29:50.720 line:80%
I've changed your medicine.

00:29:50.800 --> 00:29:52.480 line:80%
Take it easy and get some rest.

00:29:53.920 --> 00:29:56.000 line:80%
I have a few things to take care of,
so I'll be going now.

00:29:59.600 --> 00:30:01.480 line:80%
Do not move. Count to five.

00:30:02.000 --> 00:30:06.280 line:80%
Five, four, three, two, one.

00:30:10.840 --> 00:30:12.120 line:80%
Your Highness, I…

00:30:12.800 --> 00:30:14.080 line:80%
She does not wish to see you.

00:30:16.480 --> 00:30:17.320 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:30:18.680 --> 00:30:19.680 line:80%
Please wait.

00:30:20.200 --> 00:30:21.320 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:30:21.840 --> 00:30:24.360 line:80%
-Please hear me out.
-Keep your distance from Her Highness!

00:30:26.600 --> 00:30:29.080 line:80%
Your Highness, I just want to say…

00:30:29.160 --> 00:30:30.720 line:80%
-Shut the door.
-Please let me explain.

00:30:30.800 --> 00:30:31.840 line:80%
Your Highness!

00:30:31.920 --> 00:30:32.760 line:80%
Are you leaving?

00:30:33.360 --> 00:30:34.240 line:80%
I am not leaving.

00:30:35.520 --> 00:30:36.440 line:80%
Watch your foot.

00:30:45.440 --> 00:30:47.120 line:80%
-Are you hurt? Let me see.
-No, no.

00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:48.720 line:80%
I am fine.

00:30:50.120 --> 00:30:51.080 line:80%
I am fine.

00:30:54.360 --> 00:30:55.200 line:80%
You lied to me again.

00:30:58.240 --> 00:31:00.160 line:80%
I only wanted to talk to you.

00:31:01.240 --> 00:31:03.320 line:80%
Tell me honestly.
Do you have feelings for Li--

00:31:03.400 --> 00:31:04.560 line:80%
Not in the slightest!

00:31:05.160 --> 00:31:06.360 line:80%
I have no interest in him.

00:31:06.440 --> 00:31:07.720 line:80%
And none in you either.

00:31:08.400 --> 00:31:10.040 line:80%
You came all this way just to ask that?

00:31:11.680 --> 00:31:13.040 line:80%
Is there anything else?

00:31:19.880 --> 00:31:21.560 line:80%
Actually, I…

00:31:23.320 --> 00:31:24.640 line:80%
Headmaster Gongsun,

00:31:25.720 --> 00:31:27.440 line:80%
if you truly have no feelings for me,

00:31:28.560 --> 00:31:30.240 line:80%
then stop coming to see me.

00:31:42.040 --> 00:31:45.000 line:80%
THE SEA OF LEARNING HAS NO END

00:31:45.600 --> 00:31:46.920 line:80%
This foolish mouth…

00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:49.200 line:80%
Why can't I get the words out?

00:31:54.600 --> 00:31:55.680 line:80%
Changyu, go!

00:32:01.000 --> 00:32:03.400 line:80%
Changyu, why are you so distracted today?

00:32:03.480 --> 00:32:04.720 line:80%
Another round?

00:32:06.760 --> 00:32:07.600 line:80%
Come.

00:32:14.800 --> 00:32:15.640 line:80%
Forgive me, Lord Li.

00:32:18.560 --> 00:32:19.760 line:80%
Captain Fan,

00:32:19.840 --> 00:32:21.960 line:80%
I came to discuss something with you.

00:32:26.720 --> 00:32:28.040 line:80%
That live-in husband was bad enough.

00:32:28.120 --> 00:32:30.400 line:80%
This Li Menkan is even worse.

00:32:33.160 --> 00:32:34.520 line:80%
Please come back another day.

00:32:34.600 --> 00:32:36.440 line:80%
I am not in the mood today.

00:32:37.960 --> 00:32:40.840 line:80%
You've been made captain. You must learn
the terrain and military situation.

00:32:41.640 --> 00:32:43.400 line:80%
Everything's marked on the map.
Hope it helps.

00:32:44.760 --> 00:32:46.040 line:80%
If anything is unclear,

00:32:46.120 --> 00:32:47.640 line:80%
I would gladly explain.

00:32:49.480 --> 00:32:52.520 line:80%
Some people love swooping in
when there's an opening.

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:56.320 line:80%
Looks like that live-in husband
is in trouble.

00:33:00.520 --> 00:33:01.600 line:80%
In that case,

00:33:02.360 --> 00:33:03.280 line:80%
thank you, Lord Li.

00:33:04.680 --> 00:33:06.440 line:80%
If you don't want to be here, leave.

00:33:06.960 --> 00:33:09.360 line:80%
No, no. We cannot leave.

00:33:09.440 --> 00:33:10.280 line:80%
If we left,

00:33:11.800 --> 00:33:13.600 line:80%
who would protect
our captain's reputation?

00:34:20.200 --> 00:34:21.840 line:80%
-Well written!
-Is dinner ready?

00:34:22.800 --> 00:34:23.959 line:80%
That line is great.

00:34:28.039 --> 00:34:30.240 line:80%
It is getting late.
Let's stop here for today.

00:34:30.760 --> 00:34:32.240 line:80%
I've been busy lately.

00:34:32.760 --> 00:34:34.560 line:80%
I may not be able to join you
for a few days.

00:34:35.160 --> 00:34:37.039 line:80%
However, I have invited
the best instructor in Jizhou

00:34:37.120 --> 00:34:38.280 line:80%
to serve as your advisor.

00:34:38.360 --> 00:34:39.959 line:80%
You will soon grow
into the role of captain.

00:34:40.800 --> 00:34:42.320 line:80%
Then thank you, Lord Li.

00:34:42.840 --> 00:34:45.760 line:80%
Among the Enemy Stratagems
is one called "Take the Sheep in Passing".

00:34:46.999 --> 00:34:48.959 line:80%
When an opportunity appears, seize it.

00:34:49.039 --> 00:34:52.160 line:20%
Even the slightest advantage
must not be overlooked.

00:34:52.959 --> 00:34:54.200 line:80%
I know this one.

00:34:54.280 --> 00:34:56.280 line:80%
It means if I see the enemy's sheep,

00:34:56.360 --> 00:34:58.760 line:80%
I grab it and cook myself
a nice pot of mutton soup.

00:35:00.200 --> 00:35:01.280 line:80%
That is… not entirely wrong.

00:35:02.240 --> 00:35:04.000 line:80%
And this one. I know this too.

00:35:04.080 --> 00:35:05.800 line:80%
"Borrow a Knife to Kill."

00:35:05.880 --> 00:35:08.760 line:80%
It means if my weapon
gets knocked away in battle,

00:35:08.840 --> 00:35:12.320 line:80%
I borrow someone else's weapon
and chop the enemy down.

00:35:12.400 --> 00:35:14.480 line:80%
It means you do not have to act yourself.

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:17.960 line:80%
Instead, you provoke others
to eliminate the enemy for you.

00:35:18.040 --> 00:35:20.600 line:80%
That way, you preserve your own strength.

00:35:22.560 --> 00:35:23.400 line:80%
I see.

00:35:23.480 --> 00:35:26.680 line:80%
I definitely know this one.
"Watch the Fire from Across the River."

00:35:26.760 --> 00:35:27.960 line:80%
Back in my town,

00:35:28.040 --> 00:35:31.200 line:80%
rich families could watch fireworks
from right up close.

00:35:31.800 --> 00:35:35.760 line:80%
But poor kids like us
had to stand far away,

00:35:35.840 --> 00:35:38.920 line:80%
very far away,

00:35:39.000 --> 00:35:40.000 line:80%
to watch them.

00:35:41.360 --> 00:35:44.560 line:80%
It… It is not about fireworks.

00:35:47.000 --> 00:35:49.080 line:80%
It is… Let's move on.

00:35:51.560 --> 00:35:54.000 line:80%
"Point at the Berry and Curse the Ghost."
What does it mean?

00:35:54.080 --> 00:35:56.680 line:80%
It is actually "Point at the Mulberry
and Curse the Locust."

00:36:02.800 --> 00:36:04.320 line:80%
A man of upright character…

00:36:04.880 --> 00:36:05.960 line:80%
-Sir, what is--
-Changyu.

00:36:06.800 --> 00:36:07.720 line:80%
Sir.

00:36:11.200 --> 00:36:12.080 line:80%
How did the lesson go?

00:36:14.840 --> 00:36:16.960 line:80%
Captain Fan is remarkably quick-witted.

00:36:17.960 --> 00:36:19.480 line:80%
One example is all she needs.

00:36:20.200 --> 00:36:21.520 line:80%
A true talent.

00:36:21.600 --> 00:36:22.640 line:80%
You taught well, sir.

00:36:22.720 --> 00:36:23.960 line:80%
Not at all, not at all.

00:36:25.400 --> 00:36:27.120 line:80%
That will be all for today.

00:36:27.840 --> 00:36:30.120 line:80%
-I will take my leave.
-I have learned <i>Sun Zi's Art of War</i>.

00:36:30.200 --> 00:36:33.000 line:80%
Can you teach me some more
from Sun Zi's ancestors tomorrow?

00:36:34.520 --> 00:36:35.440 line:80%
Farewell.

00:36:36.520 --> 00:36:37.600 line:80%
Sir!

00:36:43.040 --> 00:36:45.480 line:80%
Find another teacher as soon as possible.

00:36:46.640 --> 00:36:47.480 line:80%
Understood.

00:36:48.120 --> 00:36:49.280 line:80%
Mr. Liu, thank you for coming.

00:36:49.360 --> 00:36:52.280 line:80%
Every one of my pupils
has become a distinguished general.

00:36:52.800 --> 00:36:56.920 line:80%
You may rest assured.
There is nothing to worry about.

00:36:58.120 --> 00:36:59.040 line:80%
Please.

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:01.200 line:80%
This way.

00:37:04.280 --> 00:37:05.720 line:80%
HALL OF LETTERS

00:37:05.800 --> 00:37:07.160 line:80%
Mr. Liu, you…

00:37:07.680 --> 00:37:09.240 line:80%
She barely recognizes the characters.

00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:11.400 line:80%
You had better find someone more capable.

00:37:11.480 --> 00:37:13.800 line:80%
-Mr. Liu, please wait.
-I truly cannot teach her.

00:37:13.880 --> 00:37:14.800 line:80%
Farewell.

00:37:14.880 --> 00:37:19.960 line:80%
THE SEA OF LEARNING HAS NO END

00:37:20.040 --> 00:37:21.680 line:80%
-My lord, he--
-Find another.

00:37:22.440 --> 00:37:25.360 line:80%
Please rest assured.
Anyone willing to learn should be taught.

00:37:26.200 --> 00:37:27.280 line:80%
Sir…

00:37:27.360 --> 00:37:28.680 line:80%
-Sir?
-I would rather starve

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:30.320 line:80%
-than attempt to teach that.
-Wait!

00:37:30.400 --> 00:37:32.240 line:80%
Anyone can be taught.

00:37:33.360 --> 00:37:34.760 line:80%
I am inadequate.

00:37:34.840 --> 00:37:36.040 line:80%
-Please have mercy
-Get up.

00:37:36.120 --> 00:37:37.840 line:80%
-and spare my life!
-Please get up.

00:37:45.440 --> 00:37:47.000 line:80%
HALL OF ARMS

00:37:57.440 --> 00:38:00.240 line:80%
SEEKING A KIND, PATIENT, STRONG
MILITARY TUTOR. THREE TAELS FOR TWO HOURS

00:38:05.160 --> 00:38:07.840 line:80%
The student you seek to teach…
Is it Captain Fan?

00:38:07.920 --> 00:38:08.840 line:80%
It is.

00:38:10.040 --> 00:38:11.200 line:80%
Sir!

00:38:14.120 --> 00:38:15.360 line:80%
My lord,

00:38:15.440 --> 00:38:17.320 line:80%
her reputation has spread
throughout the city.

00:38:17.400 --> 00:38:18.240 line:80%
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

00:38:18.320 --> 00:38:20.360 line:80%
Three taels an hour, and still no takers.

00:38:20.440 --> 00:38:21.360 line:80%
Forget it.

00:38:22.120 --> 00:38:23.480 line:80%
I will teach her myself.

00:38:24.440 --> 00:38:25.280 line:80%
What?

00:38:25.880 --> 00:38:31.000 line:20%
THREE DAYS LATER

00:38:31.080 --> 00:38:32.640 line:20%
What happened?

00:38:34.960 --> 00:38:36.200 line:80%
Captain Fan did this.

00:38:36.920 --> 00:38:39.480 line:80%
Both of you are still injured,
yet you are sparring again?

00:38:43.000 --> 00:38:44.040 line:80%
All internal injuries.

00:38:46.040 --> 00:38:47.640 line:80%
It is getting late.

00:38:48.800 --> 00:38:51.160 line:80%
Help me up. I still need to go teach her.

00:38:52.600 --> 00:38:53.840 line:80%
My lord, please rest.

00:38:54.360 --> 00:38:55.440 line:80%
Stop teaching Captain Fan.

00:38:55.520 --> 00:38:58.640 line:80%
Studying military strategy
must be done step by step. Right?

00:38:58.720 --> 00:39:00.280 line:80%
Studying strategy?

00:39:01.440 --> 00:39:02.280 line:80%
Never thought

00:39:02.360 --> 00:39:04.520 line:80%
teaching could go so wrong.

00:39:06.280 --> 00:39:07.480 line:80%
Lord Li.

00:39:10.040 --> 00:39:10.920 line:80%
Changyu.

00:39:11.560 --> 00:39:14.320 line:80%
Lord Li, no, please. Please stay seated.

00:39:16.000 --> 00:39:18.040 line:80%
Lord Li, I truly owe you an apology.

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:22.120 line:80%
Perhaps I should just study on my own.

00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:26.200 line:80%
You see, my adoptive father
is quite formidable.

00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:28.040 line:80%
He even wanted to take me as his disciple.

00:39:28.640 --> 00:39:31.240 line:80%
Do you think he is getting old
and his eyesight is failing?

00:39:32.040 --> 00:39:34.680 line:80%
You must possess a rare kind of insight.

00:39:35.560 --> 00:39:38.160 line:80%
Grand Tutor Tao must have seen
that very quality in you.

00:39:38.760 --> 00:39:40.320 line:80%
It is something I cannot compare to.

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:42.680 line:80%
I think so too.

00:39:44.920 --> 00:39:46.280 line:80%
Maybe I should just

00:39:46.360 --> 00:39:47.760 line:80%
ask him to teach me instead.

00:39:48.800 --> 00:39:51.040 line:80%
Spare the old man. Do not trouble him.

00:40:19.880 --> 00:40:21.840 line:80%
Why can I not get
any of this into my head?

00:40:23.560 --> 00:40:25.440 line:80%
Looks like I am not cut out for studying.

00:40:42.960 --> 00:40:46.160 line:80%
<i>I left some notes in red</i>
<i>between the paragraphs.</i>

00:40:47.240 --> 00:40:48.600 line:80%
<i>Read them when you have time.</i>

00:41:03.960 --> 00:41:06.520 line:80%
<i>When storms darken the sky</i>
<i>The rooster still crows</i>

00:41:07.040 --> 00:41:09.360 line:80%
<i>Having seen the graceful one</i>
<i>How could I not rejoice?</i>

00:41:10.400 --> 00:41:12.600 line:80%
<i>These lines speak</i>

00:41:12.680 --> 00:41:14.080 line:80%
<i>of storm and turmoil, rain pouring,</i>

00:41:14.600 --> 00:41:16.160 line:80%
<i>the world unsettled.</i>

00:41:17.000 --> 00:41:19.400 line:80%
<i>Yet in the midst of all that confusion,</i>

00:41:20.160 --> 00:41:21.200 line:80%
<i>you lift your eyes,</i>

00:41:22.440 --> 00:41:23.680 line:80%
<i>and suddenly, there she is.</i>

00:41:24.800 --> 00:41:27.240 line:80%
Like clouds parting,

00:41:27.840 --> 00:41:29.520 line:80%
a shaft of light falls over you.

00:41:31.040 --> 00:41:32.080 line:80%
Warm. Bright.

00:41:32.960 --> 00:41:34.720 line:80%
<i>And joy rises from somewhere inside.</i>

00:41:37.280 --> 00:41:40.040 line:80%
Why is it that when Yan Zheng teaches me,
I remember everything?

00:41:48.160 --> 00:41:50.080 line:80%
I wonder what he is doing now.

00:44:30.840 --> 00:44:34.000 line:80%
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

00:44:34.080 --> 00:44:35.000 line:80%
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang